(20, 17, 'content', 'JCM Rules & Guidelines', '<p>All of JCM projects should follow the official rules &amp; guidelines of JCM. The procedural document of JCM methodology and projects cycle as below :&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Procedure for general and specific circumstances</li>\n	<li>Approval of methodologies : From submission to approval of methodologies&nbsp;process</li>\n	<li>Registration : Public input of PDD, modalities of communication, and validation of the project</li>\n	<li>Issuance of Credit : Preparation of monitoring report, verification and request for issuance.&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>For further information : <strong><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/index.php/content/MzQ%253D/rules_%26_guidelines\">Click Here</a></strong>.</p>', NULL, 'navigation', 'active', 1, 'active', 'SysAdmin', '2016-02-27 17:05:48', 'SysAdmin', '2016-05-03 19:16:17');
