(37, 17, NULL, 'Joint Committee Result', '<p>Based on <a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document%20JCM/Rules%20&amp;%20Guidelines/JCM_ID_RoI_ver01.0.pdf\">Rules of Implementation</a>&nbsp;and <a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Rules &amp; Guidelines/JCM_ID_RoP_JC_ver02.0.pdf\">Rules of Procedures for the Joint Committee</a>&nbsp;of JCM, The Joint Committee consists of the <span style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\">echelon two&nbsp;</span>officers from&nbsp;the Government of&nbsp;Indonesia&nbsp;and Government of Japan and act as the highest decision maker in JCM implementation.&nbsp;The Joint&nbsp;Committee may develop or modify the rules and&nbsp;guidelines necessary for the implementation of the&nbsp;JCM, approve proposed methodologies, designate&nbsp;third party entities, register JCM projects, and notify&nbsp;both sides to issue credits for a JCM project.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Joint Committee meeting convenes on regular basis at least once a year. Upon&nbsp;the Joint Committee Meeting, the members from Indonesia and Japan will meet to discuss and if necessary,make&nbsp;decisions related to Joint Crediting Mechanism implementation in Indonesia. Up until now,&nbsp;Joint committee meeting have been conducted 5 times in Indonesia.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>For the Joint Committee Meeting result, you can check <a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/index.php/content/MzU%253D/joint_committee_result\"><strong>here</strong></a>.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'navigation', 'active', 2, 'active', 'SysAdmin', '2016-03-01 07:00:03', 'SysAdmin', '2016-05-03 19:16:17'),
