(39, 17, NULL, 'Environmental Impact Assessment', '<p>On The 3rd JCM Joint Committee Meeting which been held in the October 2014, one of decision made was document which can be use as project participant&#39;s reference related to necessity of Environment Impact in line with regulation in Indonesia. Moreover, this document also explained about stakeholder consultation which is conducted in Indonesia.</p>\n\n<p>The Environment Impact Assessment and Stakeholder consultation are inseparable part of PDD document. In accordance with Bilateral Cooperation Agreement about JCM for Low Carbon Growth between Indonesia and Japan, JCM Project participant should obeyed the regulations in both respected country (Indonesia and Japan)</p>\n\n<p><strong>Download Link </strong>:<strong> <a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Project Cycle/Reference_for_EIA_Stakeholder_Consultation.pdf\">JCM EIA Reference</a></strong></p>', NULL, 'navigation', 'active', 4, 'active', 'SysAdmin', '2016-03-01 07:08:16', 'SysAdmin', '2016-05-03 19:16:17'),
