(41, 29, NULL, '[Closed] Public Comment for Methodology ID_PM001 \"Power Generation by Waste Heat Recovery in Cement Industry\"', '<p>Below is the proposed methodology which has been submitted to Joint Committee Indonesia and Japan on September 2014. Secretariat has done the completeness check towards the proposed methodology and has been considered as complete.Secretariat has publicized the proposed methodology which is open for public comment in accordance with the provision on para 1.4.3 in <a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/files/index.php?action=downloadfile&amp;filename=JCM_ID_PCP_ver01.0.pdf&amp;directory=Peraturan%20dan%20Panduan&amp;\">The Joint Crediting Mechanism Project Cycle Procedure [pdf]</a></p>\n\n<p><strong>Proposed Methodology Information&nbsp;: ID_PM001</strong></p>\n\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"line-height:18px;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Proposed Methodology Title</strong></td>\n			<td>:</td>\n			<td><strong>Power Generation by Waste Heat Recovery in Cement Industry</strong></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Methodology Proponent</td>\n			<td>:</td>\n			<td>JFE Engineering Corporation .</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Proposed Methodology Document &amp; Additional Information</td>\n			<td>:</td>\n			<td>\n			<p><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Methodology/Proposed Methodology/1_WHR/Naveen_Pawar_-_Power_Generation_by_WHR_01.docx\">Proposed Methodology [Word]</a></p>\n\n			<p><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Methodology/Proposed Methodology/1_WHR/JCM_ID_F_PM_Waste-Heat-Recovery.pdf\">Proposed Methodology [PDF]</a></p>\n\n			<p><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Methodology/Proposed Methodology/1_WHR/JCM_ID_F_PMS_Waste-Heat-Recovery.xlsx\">Proposed Methodology Spreadsheet [Excel]</a></p>\n\n			<p><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Methodology/Proposed Methodology/1_WHR/JCM_ID_PM_Add_Info_Waste-Heat-Recovery.pdf\">Additional Information