(91, 17, NULL, 'Information on Registry', '<p><strong>What is Indonesia JCM Registry?</strong></p>\n\n<p>Indonesia JCM registry is a tool run by the Indonesia JCM Secretariat to save any information related to carbon credit transaction from JCM activities in Indonesia.</p>\n\n<p>Any JCM Project Participants from Indonesia side who have registered their project(s) are eligible to open an account for Indonesia JCM Registry. By having this account, project participant are allowed to request for credit issuance, credit transfer, credit cancellation and credit retirement.</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>Steps on how to open an Indonesia JCM Registry Account:</strong></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li>Download&nbsp;<a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/id/uploads/files/Document JCM/Credit Issuance/Request_Form_to_Open_Account_in_Indonesia_JCM_Registry_Form.docx\">Request Form to Open Account</a><br />\n	&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Fill in the form with the name of representative is signed by the same name as stated in participant&#39;s&nbsp;JCM Modalities of Communication<br />\n	&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Send in the document&nbsp;to the following address:<br />\n	Indonesia JCM Secretariat<br />\n	Gedung Kementerian Koordinator Bidang Perekonomian Lantai 2<br />\n	Jl. Medan Merdeka Barat No. 7<br />\n	Jakarta Pusat, DKI Jakarta, 10110<br />\n	&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>Once received, Indonesia JCM Secretariat will decide and send the result via e-mail<br />\n	&nbsp;</li>\n	<li>If the request is granted, Indonesia JCM Secretariat will open an account for the project participant<br />\n	&nbsp;</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p>For you reference, see the following sample of filled in Request Form to Open Account</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Request_Form_to_Open_Account_in_Indonesia_JCM_Registry_Form_-_Speciment_1.jpg\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Request_Form_to_Open_Account_in_Indonesia_JCM_Registry_Form_-_Speciment_1.jpg\" /></a></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', NULL