(98, 73, NULL, 'Second Call for Proposal on JCM Model Project by MOEJ in 2016', '<p style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\"><strong>Ministry of the Environment Japan (MOEJ) is calling for Model Project&nbsp;proposals for the Fiscal Year 2016 (Second Call)</strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\"><strong>The agenda is set as follows:</strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\">Start call for bid on Model Project : <strong>Sept-5, 2016</strong><br />\nDeadline for entities to submit their application :&nbsp;<strong>Dec-2, 2016</strong><br />\nPlanned date on selecting Model Project&nbsp;:<b>&nbsp;-&nbsp;</b></p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\">*</span><span style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\">Due to the limited availability of financial support, the call for proposal may close before the deadline. Candidates are encouraged to send their proposal submission at the earliest time possible.</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\">________________________________________</p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\">Please note that the JCM Model Project is the budgetary support from the government of Japan and it is our understanding that the projects selected for the Model Project are not a &ldquo;JCM project&rdquo; per se at the moment.&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n\n<p>The project participants of the selected Model Project need to go through the official JCM procedures including, for example, methodology development, validation and request for registration to the Joint Committee of JCM, where both side will discuss and consider all the matters relating to the implementation of the JCM.</p>\n\n<p>After these processes, the selected Model Project will be registered as the &ldquo;JCM project&rdquo; based on the decision of the Joint Committee.</p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\">_________________________________________</p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\">Please refer to GEC website (<a href=\"http://gec.jp/jcm/kobo/mp160905.html\">http://gec.jp/jcm/kobo/mp160905.html</a>) for further information and application documents.</p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\">For any queries regarding proposal submission, you can contact the Indonesia JCM Secretariat.</p>', NULL, 'navigation', 'active', 9, 'inactive', 'SysAdmin', '2016-09-04 18:58:45', 'SysAdmin', '2019-04-07 19:48:49'),
