(104, 73, NULL, 'Call for Proposal on City to City Collaboration Feasibility Study by MOEJ in JFY2017', '<p style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\"><strong>Ministry of the Environment Japan (MOEJ) is calling for &quot;City to City Collaboration JCM Feasibility Study proposals for the Fiscal Year 2017</strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\">This scheme encourages GHG emissions reduction activities on the city and regional scale and realizes a low carbon society by utilizing inter-city corporation between Japanese and Indonesian local government.Japanese local governments, research institutes, private companies and universities are co-operate and adjust the advanced low carbon technologies and systems to fit the local conditions to establish sustainable operation and maintenance systems in Indonesia. The agenda is set as follows:&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\">Start call for request :&nbsp;<strong>February-24, 2017</strong><br />\nDeadine for entities to submit their application :&nbsp;<strong>March-17, 2017</strong><br />\nPlanned date of selecting FS :<strong>&nbsp;End&nbsp;of March 2017</strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\">Please refer to&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.env.go.jp/press/103679.html\">http://www.env.go.jp/press/103679.html</a>&nbsp;for further information and application documents.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\">Please also send project information using Project Idea Note format to&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:secretariat@jcmindonesia.com\">secretariat@jcmindonesia.com</a>(please refer to :&nbsp;<a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/index.php/content/MzA%253D/propose_a_project\">jcm.ekon.go.id</a>).</p>', NULL, 'navigation', 'inactive', 8, 'inactive', 'SysAdmin', '2017-02-27 23:54:08', 'SysAdmin', '2019-04-07 19:48:49');
