(105, 73, NULL, 'Call for Proposal on JCM Model Project by MOEJ in 2017', '<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Ministry of the Environment Japan (MOEJ) is calling for Model Project&nbsp;proposals for the Fiscal Year 2017</strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">The agenda is set as follows:</strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Start call for bid on Model Project :&nbsp;<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">April 7th, 2017</strong><br style=\"font-size: inherit;\" />\nDeadline for entities to submit their application :&nbsp;<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">May 15th, 2017</strong><br style=\"font-size: inherit;\" />\nPlanned date on selecting Model Project&nbsp;:<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">&nbsp;-&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Candidates are encouraged to send their proposal submission at the earliest time possible. The submission should be send to:</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Global Environment Centre Foundation Tokyo Office<br />\n4th Floor Hongo Ozeki Bldg., 3-19-4 Hongo Bunkyo-ku,<br />\nTokyo 113-0033, Japan</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">A complete proposal must be submitted to GEC Tokyo Office in a sealed envelope by registered mail, private courier service or by hand-delivery. Proposals submitted by fax, e-mail or via Internet&nbsp;will be rejected.</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Abel, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\">More information on the guidelines for proposal submission can be downloaded&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/(tentative)2017_Guidelines_for_Submitting_Proposals.pdf\" style=\"font-family: Abel, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\">here</a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Abel, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\">.</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Abel, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\">Please refer to GEC website (</span><a href=\"http://gec.jp/jcm/kobo/mp170407.html\" style=\"font-family: Abel, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\">http://gec.jp/jcm/kobo/mp170407.html</a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Abel, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; text-align: justify;\">) for further information and application documents.</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">________________________________________</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Please note that the JCM Model Project is the budgetary support from the government of Japan and it is our understanding that the projects selected for the Model Project are not a &ldquo;JCM project&rdquo; per se at the moment.&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">The project participants of the selected Model Project need to go through the official JCM procedures including, for example, methodology development, validation and request for registration to the Joint Committee of JCM, where both side will discuss and consider all the matters relating to the implementation of the JCM.</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">After these processes, the selected Model Project will be registered as the &ldquo;JCM project&rdquo; based on the decision of the Joint Committee.</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">_________________________________________</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'navigation', 'inactive', 7, 'inactive', 'SysAdmin', '2017-04-07 00:30:06', 'SysAdmin', '2019-04-07 19:48:49'),
