(126, 73, NULL, 'Call for Proposal on JCM Model Project by MOEJ in 2018', '<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Ministry of the Environment Japan (MOEJ) is calling for Model Project&nbsp;proposals for the Fiscal Year 2018</strong></p>\n\n<p>JCM is a bilateral cooperation between Government of Indonesia and Government of Japan to implement low carbon development activities in Indonesia through an incentive given by Government of Japan.&nbsp;JCM activities covers many sectoral scope, including energy efficiency, renewable energy, deforestation and forest degradation, waste management, fugitive emission, and manufacture industry.</p>\n\n<p>In order to support the implementation of candidate JCM projects, Ministry of the Environment, Japan (hereinafter referred to as &ldquo;MOEJ&rdquo;) has launched the &ldquo;JCM Model Projects (hereinafter referred to as &ldquo;model project&rdquo;),&rdquo; which includes collaboration with projects supported by the Japan International Cooperation Agency and other governmental-affiliated financial institution.</p>\n\n<p>The financial support that can be given through the scheme is up to 50% of total investment of the model project.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">The schedule of the proposal submission is set as follows:</strong></p>\n\n<p>Start&nbsp;call&nbsp;for&nbsp;bid&nbsp;on Model&nbsp;Project :&nbsp;<strong>6 April 2018</strong><br />\nDeadline for entities to submit their&nbsp;application :&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Monday, 14 May 2018 at 12:00 (Japan Standard Time)</strong><br />\nPreliminary selection of JCM Model Projects: <strong>Around end of June, 2018&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Candidates are encouraged to send their proposal submission at the earliest time possible. The submission should&nbsp;be send&nbsp;to:</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Global Environment Centre Foundation Tokyo Office<br />\n4th Floor Hongo Ozeki Bldg., 3-19-4 Hongo Bunkyo-ku,<br />\nTokyo 113-0033, Japan</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;(GEC accepts proposals 10:00-12:00 and 13:00 &ndash; 17:00 (except Saturdays, Sundays and public holidays)</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">A complete proposal must be submitted to GEC Tokyo Office in a sealed envelope by registered mail, private courier service or by hand-delivery. Proposals submitted by fax, e-mail or via Internet&nbsp;will be rejected.</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">More information on the guidelines for proposal submission can be downloaded&nbsp;<a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Rules &amp; Guidelines - Forms/(tentative)2018_Guidelines_for_Submitting_Proposals.pdf\">here</a>.</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Please refer to GEC website (<a href=\"http://gec.jp/jcm/kobo/mp180406/\">http://gec.jp/jcm/kobo/mp180406/</a>) for further information and application documents.</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">________________________________________</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 20.8px; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: 1.6em; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Please note that the JCM Model Project is the budgetary support from the government of Japan and it is our understanding that the projects selected for the Model Project are not a &ldquo;JCM project&rdquo; per se at the moment.&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">The project participants of the selected Model Project need to go through the official JCM procedures including, for example, methodology development, validation&nbsp;and&nbsp;request for registration to the Joint Committee of JCM, where both&nbsp;side&nbsp;will discuss and consider all the matters relating to the implementation of the JCM.</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; font-family: Abel, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">After these processes, the selected Model Project will be registered as the &ldquo;JCM project&rdquo; based on the decision of the Joint Committee.</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 16px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; li