(33, 5, NULL, 'Persetujuan Kerjasama', '<p style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\"><span style=\"text-align: center;\">Dokumen Persetujuan Kerjasama Joint&nbsp;Crediting Mechanism (JCM) antara Indonesia dan Jepang ditandatangani pada tanggal&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 20.8px; text-align: center;\">7&nbsp;Agustus 2013 oleh Menteri Luar Negeri, Mr. Fumio Kishida&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em; text-align: center;\">dan pada&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em; text-align: center;\">26 Agustus 2013 oleh&nbsp;Menteri Koordinator Bidang Perekonomian</span><span style=\"line-height: 20.8px; text-align: center;\">,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.6em; text-align: center;\">Bapak&nbsp;Hatta Rajasa.&nbsp;Dokumen ini berfungsi sebagai bukti kerjasama Indonesia&nbsp;dan Jepang untuk&nbsp;skema Joint Crediting Mechanism.&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\"><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Reference/JCM_Bilateral_Cooperation_(signed_2_ministers).pdf\"><strong><span style=\"text-align: center;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/JCM scheme picture/bilateralcooperation.png\" /></span></strong></a></p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\"><strong style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\"><span style=\"text-align: center;\">Download :&nbsp;<a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Reference/JCM_Bilateral_Cooperation_(signed_2_ministers).pdf\">JCM Bilateral Cooperation Document - 2013</a></span></strong></p>', NULL, 'navigation', 'active', 1, 'active', 'SysAdmin', '2016-03-01 02:02:42', 'SysAdmin', '2017-07-04 21:18:51'),
(34, 5, NULL, 'Aturan & Pedoman JCM', '<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"1\">\n	<thead>\n		<tr>\n			<th scope=\"col\">No</th>\n			<th scope=\"col\">Judul Dokumen &amp; Deskripsi</th>\n			<th scope=\"col\">Download</th>\n		</tr>\n	</thead>\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>1.</strong></td>\n			<td>\n			<p><strong>Joint Crediting Mechanism Guidelines for Developing Project Design Document and Monitoring Report Ver03.0</strong></p>\n\n			<p><span style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\">&quot;<em>Joint Crediting Mechanism Guidelines for Developing Project Design Document and Monitoring Report</em>&quot; (selanjutnya disebut sebagai&nbsp;&quot;Pedoman ini&quot;) ditujukan untuk membantu&nbsp;partisipan&nbsp;proyek dalam menyusun<em>&nbsp;Joint Crediting Mechanism </em>(selanjutnya disebut sebagai&nbsp;&quot;JCM&quot;)<em> project design document </em>(selanjutnya disebut sebagai&nbsp;&quot;PDD&quot;) dan laporan <em>monitoring</em>.</span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/id/uploads/files/Document JCM/Rules &amp; Guidelines/JCM_ID_GL_PDD_MR_ver03.0.pdf\">Download</a></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\n			<td><strong>Project Design Document Form ver02.0</strong></td>\n			<td><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/id/uploads/files/Document JCM/Rules &amp; Guidelines - Forms/JCM_ID_F_PDD_ver02.0.docx\">Download</a></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>2.</strong></td>\n			<td>\n			<p><strong>Joint Crediting Mechinism Guidelines for Developing Proposed Methodology ver02.0</strong></p>\n\n			<p><span style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\">&quot;Pedoman <em>Joint Crediting Mechanism </em>untuk Menyusun Usulan Metodologi&quot; (selanjutnya disebut sebagai&nbsp;&quot;Pedoman ini&quot;) ditujukan untuk membantu tiap sisi atau partisipan proyek&nbsp;(selanjutnya disebut sebagai&nbsp;&quot;pengusul metodologi&quot;) dalam menyiapkan usulan metodologi untuk&nbsp;<em>Joint Crediting Mechanism</em>&nbsp;(selanjutnya disebut sebagai&nbsp;&quot;JCM&quot;) (selanjutnya disebut sebagai&nbsp;&quot;usulan metodologi&quot;)</span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/id/uploads/files/Document JCM/Rules &amp; Guidelines/JCM_ID_GL_PM_ver02.0.pdf\">Download</a></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\n			<td><strong>JCM Proposed Methodology Form ver01.0 &amp; Spreadsheet Form ver01.1</strong></td>\n			<td>\n			<p><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Rules &amp; Guidelines - Forms/JCM_ID_F_PM_ver01.0.doc\" target=\"_blank\">P</a><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Rules &amp; Guidelines - Forms/JCM_ID_F_PM_ver01.0.doc\">M_Form Ver01.0</a></p>\n\n			<p><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Rules &amp; Guidelines - Forms/after JC 6/JCM_ID_F_PMS_ver01.1.xlsx\">PMS_Form Ver01.1</a></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>3.</strong></td>\n			<td>\n			<p><strong>Joint Crediting Mechanism Guidelines for Designation of a Third-Party Entity ver03.1</strong></p>\n\n			<p>Pedoman ini berlaku untuk entitas kandidat, entitas pihak ketiga, Komite Bersama dan Sekretariat JCM&nbsp;(selanjutnya disebut sebagai&nbsp;&quot;sekretariat&quot;) sehubungan dengan penunjukan, penundaan&nbsp;dan&nbsp;pengunduran diri dari Entitas Pihak Ketiga.&nbsp;</p>\n			</td>\n			<td><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Rules &amp; Guidelines/after JC 6/JCM_ID_GL_TPE_ver03.1.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Download</a></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\n			<td><strong>JCM&nbsp;Application Form for Designation as a Third-Party Entity&nbsp;ver02.0&nbsp;</strong></td>\n			<td><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Rules &amp; Guidelines - Forms/JCM_ID_F_TPE_ver02.0.docx\" target=\"_blank\">Download</a></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>4.</strong></td>\n			<td>\n			<p><strong>Joint Crediting Mechanism Guidelines for Validation and Verification ver01.0</strong></p>\n\n			<p>Pedoman ini&nbsp;berlaku untuk entitas pihak ketiga&nbsp;(selanjutnya disebut sebagai &quot;TPEs&quot;) yang sudah dibawah perjanjian kontraktual&nbsp;dengan partisipan proyek untuk memvalidasi atau memverifikasi proyek-proyek JCM yang ada berdasarkan metodologi JCM yang sebelumnya sudah disetujui oleh Komite Bersama.</p>\n			</td>\n			<td><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Rules &amp; Guidelines/JCM_ID_GL_VV_ver01.0.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Download</a></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\n			<td><strong>JCM Validation&nbsp;</strong><strong>Form ver01.0&nbsp;&amp; Verification Report&nbsp;Form ver01.1</strong></td>\n			<td>\n			<p><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Rules &amp; Guidelines - Forms/JCM_ID_F_Val_Rep_ver01.0.doc\" target=\"_blank\">Download Validation Report Form</a></p>\n\n			<p><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/id/uploads/files/Document JCM/Rules &amp; Guidelines - Forms/JCM_ID_F_Vrf_Rep_ver01.1.docx\">Download Verification Report Form</a></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>5.</strong></td>\n			<td>\n			<p><strong>Joint Crediting Mechanism Project Cycle Procedure ver05.1</strong></p>\n\n			<p>Prosedur-prosedur berikut mendeskripsikan langkah-langkah administratif yang harus diikuti oleh partisipan proyek, entitas pihak ketiga (selanjutnya disebut sebagai &quot;TPE&quot;), pemangku kepentingan lainnya, Komite Bersama, Sekretariat dan kedua belah sisi untuk menyetujui metodologi, registrasi proyek JCM, penerbitan kredit, dan tindakan terkait.</p>\n			</td>\n			<td>\n			<p><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Rules &amp; Guidelines/JCM_ID_PCP_ver05.1.pdf\">Download</a></p>\n\n			<p><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Rules &amp; Guidelines/JCM_ID_PCP_ver05.1_track.pdf\">Histori</a></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\n			<td><strong>JCM Modalities of Communication Statement Form ver01.0</strong></td>\n			<td><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Rules &amp; Guidelines - Forms/JCM_ID_F_MoC_ver01_0.docx\" target=\"_blank\">Download</a></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\n			<td><strong>JCM Project Registration Request Form ver01.0</strong></td>\n			<td><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Rules &amp; Guidelines - Forms/JCM_ID_F_Reg_Req_ver01.0.doc\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\">Download</span></a></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\n			<td><strong>JCM Credit Issuance Request Form ver03.1</strong></td>\n			<td>\n			<p><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Rules &amp; Guidelines - Forms/JCM_ID_F_Iss_Req_ver03.1.pdf\">PDF</a><br />\n			<span style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\"><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Rules &amp; Guidelines - Forms/JCM_ID_F_Iss_Req_ver03.1.docx\">W</a></span><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Rules &amp; Guidelines - Forms/JCM_ID_F_Iss_Req_ver03.1.docx\"><span style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\">ord</span></a></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\n			<td><strong>JCM Approved Methodology Revision Request Form ver01.0</strong></td>\n			<td><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Rules &amp; Guidelines - Forms/JCM_ID_F_AMR_Req_ver01.0.docx\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\">Download</span></a></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\n			<td><strong>JCM Post-Registration Changes Request Form ver01.0</strong></td>\n			<td><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Rules &amp; Guidelines - Forms/JCM_ID_F_PRC_Req_ver01.0.docx\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\">Download</span></a></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\n			<td><strong>JCM Registration Request Withdrawal Form ver01.0</strong></td>\n			<td><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Rules &amp; Guidelines - Forms/JCM_ID_F_RW_Req_ver01.0.docx\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"lin