(131, 29, NULL, '[Closed] Public Comment for Revised Approved Methodology ID_PM025 \"Replacement of conventional burners with regenerative burners for aluminum holding furnaces\" 3 July-17 July 2018', '<p style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\">Below is the revised&nbsp;methodology&nbsp;which has been submitted&nbsp;to&nbsp;Joint Committee Indonesia and&nbsp;Japan&nbsp;on 29 June 2018. Secretariat has done the completeness check towards the revised methodology and has been considered as complete.&nbsp;Secretariat has&nbsp;publicized the revised methodology which&nbsp;is open for&nbsp;public comment in accordance with the provision on para&nbsp;1.4.3 in&nbsp;<a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/files/index.php?action=downloadfile&amp;filename=JCM_ID_PCP_ver01.0.pdf&amp;directory=Peraturan%20dan%20Panduan&amp;\">The Joint Crediting Mechanism Project Cycle Procedure [pdf]</a></p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\"><strong>Revised Approved&nbsp;Methodology Information</strong></p>\n\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"line-height: 21px;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Methodology No.&nbsp;</strong></td>\n			<td><strong>:</strong></td>\n			<td><strong>ID_PM025</strong></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Revised Approved Methodology No.</td>\n			<td>:</td>\n			<td>ID_AM009</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Approved Methodology Title</strong></td>\n			<td><strong>:</strong></td>\n			<td><strong><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, &quot;Nimbus Sans L&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">Replacement of conventional burners with regenerative burners for aluminum holding furnaces</span></strong></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Methodology Proponent</td>\n			<td>:</td>\n			<td>Institute for Global Environmental Strategies</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"width: 239px;\">Proposed Methodology Document &amp; Additional Information</td>\n			<td>:</td>\n			<td>\n			<p><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Methodology/Revised Methodology/PM_ID025/JCM_ID_PM025_PM