(144, 29, NULL, '[CLOSED] - Komentar Publik untuk Metodologi ID_PM028 \"Electricity generation by installation of run-of-river hydro power generation system(s) in Indonesia', '<p style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\">Dibawah ini merupakan usulan metodologi yang telah disubmit ke Komite Bersama&nbsp;Indonesia dan&nbsp;Jepang pada 11 Maret 2019. Sekretariat telah melakukan pemeriksaan kelengkapan terhadap usulan metodologi dan&nbsp;telah dianggap lengkap. Sekretariat telah mempublikasikan setiap&nbsp;usulan&nbsp;metodologi&nbsp;terbuka untuk komentar publik sesuai dengan ketentuan pada baris pasal&nbsp;1.4.3&nbsp;<a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/id/uploads/files/Document JCM/Rules &amp; Guidelines/JCM_ID_PCP_ver05.0,_(for_public_comments)_subsection_1.4.3._of_the_Joint_Crediting_Mechanism_Project_Cycle_Procedure.pdf\"><span style=\"font-style: italic;\">The Joint Crediting Mechanism Project Cycle Procedure [pdf]</span></a></p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height: 20.8px;\"><strong>Informasi Usulan Metodologi&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\">:&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"line-height: 1.6em;\">ID_PM028</strong></p>\n\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"line-height: 21px;\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td><strong>Judul Usulan Metodologi</strong></td>\n			<td>:</td>\n			<td><strong>Electricity generation by installation of run-of-river hydro power generation system(s) in Indonesia</strong></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Nama Pengusul Metodologi</td>\n			<td>:</td>\n			<td>Institute for Global Environmental Strategies</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>Dokumen Usulan Metodologi &amp; Informasi Tambahan</td>\n			<td>:</td>\n			<td>\n			<p><a href=\"http://jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Methodology/Proposed Methodology/28_Run-of-river hydro/JCM_ID_PM028_PM.pdf\">Usulan Metodologi&nbsp;[PDF]</a></p>\n\n			<p><a href=\"//jcm.ekon.go.id/en/uploads/files/Document JCM/Methodology/Proposed Methodology/28_Run-of-river hydro/JCM_ID_PM028_PMS.xlsx\">Lembar Usulan Metodologi&nbsp;[Exce